OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax     F387A1753986900
OL,3,CThird of youth crimes committed by
OL,4,Csame ten children in Jersey
OL,6,F"That offers us a real opportunity to
OL,7,Fuse the Youth Justice Roadmap to
OL,8,Freally target those young people who
OL,9,Fare repeatedly committing crimes."
OL,11,FChief Officer Smith also addresses
OL,12,Fconcerns about the number of children
OL,13,Fbeing manipulated into handling
OL,14,Fillegal drugs after a major network
OL,15,Fwas exposed, which involved those as
OL,16,Fyoung as 12.
OL,18,FHe says: "It was big news. But when
OL,19,Fit's big news, it tells me it's rare.
OL,1,W~+$z5~{4~k4~k4~sj5  hws         G3/5
