CT,2,C
PS,c000
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax     F387A1753986900
OL,3,CThird of youth crimes committed by
OL,4,Csame ten children in Jersey
OL,6,F"But as I've said repeatedly in the
OL,7,Ftime that I've been Chief here, the
OL,8,Fbiggest threat we have to the island
OL,9,Fis complacency.
OL,11,F"So whilst it is rare, that doesn't
OL,12,Fmean to say we're not constantly
OL,13,Fvigilant."
OL,15,FThe Jersey Police Authority have
OL,16,Fraised concerns over government
OL,17,Ffunding, but Chief Officer Smith says
OL,18,Fthere has to be a balance.
