OL,6,FHe explains: "We still live in a very
OL,7,Flow crime area, around 3,000 crimes a
OL,8,Fyear.
OL,10,F"No police chief I know is ever going
OL,11,Fto say they need less money.
OL,13,F"But we also recognise the Government
OL,14,Fis looking to reduce costs and we want
OL,15,Fto be part of that. We are having
OL,16,Fthose discussions about using
OL,17,Fresources, so islanders get really
OL,18,Fgood bang for their buck."
